title: Thom Hartmann Program - October 10 2013
description:
October 10, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: Brunch With Bernie (Thursday edition) - Senator Bernie Sanders (I-VT) takes your calls

Hour Two: Latest on the shutdown - Senator Sherrod Brown (D-OH) / Plus, Climate Change - the PETM shocker you need to know - Dr. Joe Romm, Climate Progress

Hour Three: We're bringing in a hostage negotiator - David Selig, Selig & Associates / Plus, Mother effing truckers join Thom - Zeeda Andrews, Ride for the Constitution
